name: Voltas 320 Ltr Single Door Horizontal Chest Freezer (White)
description: Safely store your perishable foods in the Voltas 320-Litre SD Soft Look Horizontal Chest Cooler. Built to last, it has a corrosion-resistant, powder-coated outer body for durability and a stucco aluminium inner liner for hygiene. It features castors to ensure ease of movement. The spring-loaded hinges of its doors allow easy opening and closing. With elegant door trims, this cooler will be a stylish yet functional addition to any setup. 320 Litres Capacity. Castor Wheels for Easy Transportation. CFC-Free Insulation for Environment Protection. Powder Painted Body for Glossy Finish
